ts on PS5 Slim consoles. If you grab one--or you already have a PS5--be sure try one of the limited-time 30th Anniversary dynamic PS5 themes Sony launched today.PS5 Slim -- $425 ($500)PS5 Slim: Fortnite Cobalt Star Edition -- $425 ($500) | Also at PS DirectPS5 Slim Digital with NBA 2K25 -- $375 ($500)PS5 Slim Digital: Fortnite Cobalt Star Edition -- $375 ($500) | Also at PS DirectPS5 Slim Digital -- $375 ($450)PlayStation VR 2 Horizon: Call of the Mountain Bundle -- $350 ($600) | Also at Target and PS DirectPlayStation VR 2 -- $350 ($550) | Also at Target and PS DirectDualSense Controllers -- $55 ($75-$80) | Also at Walmart and Best BuyPS5 Console Covers -- Save $10 PS5PS5 DigitalPS5 SlimPowerA Accessory Bundle for PlayStation Portal -- $75 | Preorder, releases December 17More Gaming Handheld Cyber Monday DealsIf you're looking for more portable gaming deals available during Cyber Monday, you can pick up the Windows-powered Lenovo Go and Asus ROG Ally handheld gaming PCs at big discounts right now. There are also officially licensed retro handhelds from My Arcade that are up to 50% off, and include classic games like Tetris, Mega Man, Street Fighter 2, and more.Lenovo Legion Go -- $485 ($700)Asus ROG Ally Z1 (512GB) -- $350 ($500)Asus ROG Ally Z1 Extreme (512GB) -- $500 ($650) | $450 for My Best Buy membersAsus ROG Ally X (1TB) -- $700 ($800)My Arcade Tetris Pocket Player Pro -- $22.49 ($40)My Arcade Tetris Go Gamer -- $20 ($30)My Arcade Atari 100-in-1 Pocket Player Pro -- $34.74 ($40)My Arcade Galaga and Galaxian Pocket Player Pro -- $30 ($40)My Arcade Mega Man 1-6 Pocket Player Pro -- $37 ($40)My Arcade Ms. Pac-Man Pocket Player Pro -- $28 ($40)My Arcade Pac-Man Joystick Player -- $30 ($50)My Arcade Pac-Man Pocket Player Pro -- $28 ($40)My Arcade Super Street Fighter 2 Pocket Player Pro -- $32 ($40)For more Cyber Monday discounts, be sure to check GameSpot's Deal Hub for the latest bargains on video games, electronics, and more. Indiana Jones And The Great Circle 