ame\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;seamlessScrollPage\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;searchDim\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;}\" data-track-page-event=\"{\u0026#34;eventName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Monetization Link Clicked\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantPrice\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://go.skimresources.com/?id=225336X1707200\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;xcust=subid_value\u0026amp;url=https://direct.playstation.com/en-us/buy-accessories/playstation-portal-remote-player-30th-anniversary-limited-edition\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e                        \u003c/p\u003e              \u003cp\u003ePlayStation Direct is the official PlayStation retail portal, so you\u0026#39;re getting the device directly from Sony. PS Direct requires you to sign in with your PSN account before you can buy. All orders are eligible for free standard shipping.\u003c/p\u003e                      \u003c/div\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eThe PlayStation Portal is a handheld device used for streaming gameplay directly from your PS5 over Wi-Fi. The device does not play games natively. Design-wise, it looks like a DualSense PS5 controller with an 8-inch LCD screen. The Portal supports DualSense features like adaptive triggers and haptic feedback and can stream gameplay at up to 1080p resolutions and 60fps. Like other 30th Anniversary PlayStation devices, this version of the Portal features a gray color scheme and colored face buttons that resemble the original PlayStation 1 console and its DualShock controller.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eStocks are limited, and given how popular all the 30th Anniversary consoles and accessories are, chances are the Portal will sell out soon. If you\u0026#39;ve been considering buying one, now is the time.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eIf you grab a 30th Anniversary PS Portal, you might want to check out the upcoming \u003cstrong\u003eofficial PS Portal accessories bundle\u003c/strong\u003e available at \u003ca href=\"https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%2F%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-accessories%2Fpowera-accessory-bundle-for-playstation-portal-remote-player\u0026amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fplaystation-portal-30th-anniversary-edition-restocked-on-cyber-monday%2F1100-6528185%2F\u0026amp;event_type=click\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003ePlayStation Direct\u003c/a\u003e. The bundle launches December 17 and includes an officially licensed third-party USB charging station, carrying case, and screen protector from PowerA for $75.\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eMore PlayStation Deals\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eWhile the 30th Anniversary PS5 consoles and DualSense controllers are sold out, there are still plenty of PlayStation deals left over from Black Friday and Cyber Monday, including discounts on PS5 Slim consoles. If you grab one--or you already have a PS5--be sure try one of the \u003ca href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/playstation-30th-anniversary-kicks-off-with-nostalgic-ps5-themes-and-the-cranberries/1100-6528157/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6528157\"\u003elimited-time 30th Anniversary dynamic PS5 themes\u003c/a\u003e Sony launched today.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%2F%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-consoles%2Fplaystation5-console-model-group-slim\u0026amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fplaystation-portal-30th-anniversary-edition-restocked-on-cyber-monday%2F1100-6528185%2F\u0026amp;event_type=click\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blan